org.apache.flink.streaming.api.transformations

类 TwoInputTransformation<IN1,IN2,OUT>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.streaming.api.transformations.StreamTransformation<OUT>
      • org.apache.flink.streaming.api.transformations.TwoInputTransformation<IN1,IN2,OUT>
  • 类型参数:
    IN1 - The type of the elements in the first input StreamTransformation
    IN2 - The type of the elements in the second input StreamTransformation
    OUT - The type of the elements that result from this TwoInputTransformation

    @Internal
public class TwoInputTransformation<IN1,IN2,OUT>
extends StreamTransformation<OUT>
    This Transformation represents the application of a TwoInputStreamOperator to two input StreamTransformations. The result is again only one stream.

        Creates a new TwoInputTransformation from the given inputs and operator.
        参数:
        input1 - The first input StreamTransformation
        input2 - The second input StreamTransformation
        name - The name of the StreamTransformation, this will be shown in Visualizations and the Log
        operator - The TwoInputStreamOperator
        outputType - The type of the elements produced by this Transformation
        parallelism - The parallelism of this Transformation
